OL,3,CMum of boy, 3, who died of sepsis
OL,4,Ccriticises 'chaotic' hospital care
OL,6,FThe mother of a three-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied from Sepsis has told the inquest
OL,8,Finto his death that he was not given
OL,9,Fantibiotics early enough and doctors
OL,10,Ffailed to recognise the condition.
OL,12,FOscar Neillings died at Chesterfield
OL,13,FRoyal Hospital on 8 November 2023
OL,14,Fafter contracting a Strep A infection.
OL,16,FAt the inquest into his death at
OL,17,FChesterfield Coroner's Court on
OL,18,FWednesday, jurors were told Oscar
OL,19,Fdeveloped a cold about a week before
OL,20,Fhis death from which he never
OL,21,Frecovered.
