OL,3,CMum of boy, 3, who died of sepsis
OL,4,Ccriticises 'chaotic' hospital care
OL,6,FAs his symptoms worsened, his parents
OL,7,Fcalled 111 twice in the days leading
OL,8,Fup to his death and he was given
OL,9,Fappointments with two separate out-of-
OL,10,Fhours GPs.
OL,12,FBoth doctors said he had a viral
OL,13,Finfection and did not think he needed
OL,14,Fto be referred to hospital, the court
OL,15,Fwas told.
OL,17,FOscar continued to deteriorate,
OL,18,Fsuffering from abdominal pain,
OL,19,Fvomiting, and breathing difficulties.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
