OL,3,CMum of boy, 3, who died of sepsis
OL,4,Ccriticises 'chaotic' hospital care
OL,6,FShe said: "His personality was
OL,7,Finfectious. He had confidence I could
OL,8,Fonly dream of."
OL,10,FMs Neillings also criticised the care
OL,11,Fhe had been given, both by the second
OL,12,Fout-of-hours GP and at the hospital.
OL,14,FShe said she thought something should
OL,15,Fhad been done after the second
OL,16,Fappointment, telling the court: "It's
OL,17,Fmadness how he was sent home diagnosed
OL,18,Fwith a viral infection but obviously
OL,19,Fin pain."
