OL,3,CMum of boy, 3, who died of sepsis
OL,4,Ccriticises 'chaotic' hospital care
OL,6,FShe said at the hospital no-one
OL,7,Frecognised that Oscar had sepsis and
OL,8,Fdescribed the care he received as
OL,9,F"chaotic" with a lack of communication
OL,10,Fand leadership.
OL,12,FMs Neillings told the court: "It was
OL,13,Fso unorganised - I didn't know what
OL,14,Fwas going on."
OL,16,FShe added: "There was a lack of
OL,17,Fleadership ` no-one took control
OL,18,Fthroughout the day. He didn't get the
OL,19,Fantibiotics when he needed them, they
OL,20,Fmissed their timescales for that."
